    "attributes": {
        "action": "Launch an inquiry to identify the long-term solutions to current energy crisis",
        "additional_details": "It needs to be addressed at the root cause rather than using temporary measures that provide limited respite from the massive increases in price.\r\n \r\nMany people will be left without food and warmth if the current crisis is not addressed urgently. Most of the nation are worried about how they are going to manage to afford the significant increase on their bills. People should not be worrying about these extortionate prices. We have already seen significant increases during the summer months. The further increases will inevitably have a knock on effect on all products in the supply chain as we've already seen.",
        "background": "The Government needs to hold an inquiry to address the current energy crisis, and to identify a long-term solution that works in favour or the people.",
